I am writing to apply for the (Junior) Insights \& Analytics Consultant position within your Business Insights team. As a Data Analyst with more than five years of experience turning business questions into dashboards, KPI frameworks, and actionable insights, I am excited by the opportunity to support data-informed decision-making across The Quality Group's digital business.

